0.title: Total requests
0.query:
timeseries avg(dt.runtime.go.http.requests), by: { dt.entity.process_group_instance }
| fieldsAdd runtime.go.http.requests = ArrayAvg(`avg(dt.runtime.go.http.requests)`)
| sort runtime.go.http.requests desc
| limit 20
